    <h1 class="display-lg post-title">Special Financing: Mortgage Solutions for Complex Home Buying Situations</h1>
    <div class="post-byline"><span class="mono">By Jim Blackburn · NMLS #1072866</span><span class="post-byline__sep">·</span><time datetime="2025-11-12">2025-11-12</time></div>
  </header>

  <figure class="container-prose post-hero">
    <img src="/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/ChatGPT-Image-Nov-12-2025-12_59_09-AM.png" alt="Special Financing: Mortgage Solutions for Complex Home Buying Situations" width="1200" height="675" loading="eager" />
  </figure>

